%N A395782 Expansion of (Sum_{k>=0} binomial(4*k+1,k) * x^k)^4.
%F A395782 a(n) = Sum_{i,j,k,l >= 0 and i+j+k+l=n} binomial(4*i+1,i) * binomial(4*j+1,j) * binomial(4*k+1,k) * binomial(4*l+1,l).
%F A395782 G.f.: B(x)^4 where B(x) is the g.f. of A052203.
%F A395782 a(n) = Sum_{k=0..n} 3^k * binomial(k+2,2) * binomial(4*n+7,n-k).
%F A395782 a(n) = Sum_{k=0..n} 4^k * binomial(k+2,2) * binomial(4*n+4-k,n-k).
%F A395782 a(0) = 1; a(n) = (1/n) * Sum_{k=0..n-1} (4*k+20) * 3^k * binomial(k+3,3) * binomial(4*n+7,n-1-k).
%F A395782 a(0) = 1; a(n) = (1/n) * Sum_{k=0..n-1} (3*k+20) * 4^k * binomial(k+3,3) * binomial(4*n+3-k,n-1-k).
%o A395782 (PARI) a(n) = sum(k=0, n, 3^k*binomial(k+2, 2)*binomial(4*n+7, n-k));
%Y A395782 Cf. A052203, A308523, A395781.
